  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\">At 14th level, you gain the ability to augment your weapons with your barrier. As a bonus action, you can expend up to 3 barrier ticks to grant one weapon you're carrying a bonus to damage rolls equal to the number of barrier ticks spent. The additional damage is force damage and can detonate primed targets. This effect lasts 1 minute.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; margin-top: -0.8em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #191813; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid; text-indent: 1em;\">Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
